Create repository:
svnadmin create /home/afrank/Dropbox/svn-repos

List projects in repository:
svn list file:///home/afrank/Dropbox/svn-repos

Remove projects from repository:
svn delete file:///home/afrank/Dropbox/svn-repos/PROJNAME -m "gone"

Checking out project from repository:
svn co file:///home/afrank/Dropbox/svn-repos/PROJNAME/trunk PROJNAME
svn co file:///C:/Dropbox/svn-repos/faamath/trunk faamath

Create project in repository:
svn import PATH file:///home/afrank/Dropbox/svn-repos/PROJNAME/trunk -m "first version"
svn import PATH file:///C:/Dropbox/svn-repos/PROJNAME/trunk -m "first version"

